channel.title: Tornait - Sunburst (Electro House)
channel.description:
Hey guys, tornait here
I have released a new track for your listening pleasure. Hope you enjoy— and your comments are appreciated. Oh, it's my first official track of 2019. Gotta start the year off right, yeah, yeah!
[![Untitled%20design-1|500x500](upload://cluay4p3xbt46hG7LZUim89rO2d.png)](https://soundcloud.com/tornait-jaybird/sunburst)
Click on the pic to go to the track, y'all

item.dc:creator: iammane
item.description:
Dig it - really like the art, fits the tone of the song nicely. Font work on point!

Love the parts with the vibrato on the lead, awesome. All in all, high energy, great flow.

REALLY like the art the more I look at it lol, the colors are awesome
